Kay Williams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kay_Williams 0 Kathleen Gretchen "Kay" Williams (August 7, 1916 – May 25, 1983) was an American actress. She appeared in numerous uncredited bit parts throughout the 1940s before playing Hazel Dawn in George Cukor's The Actress (1953).
